file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: "API"
  version: "1.0.0"
  contact:
    name: Starkina Maria
    email: starkina@surfstudio.ru

components:
  securitySchemes:
    bearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
      bearerFormat: JWT 

security:
  - bearerAuth: []

paths:
  /user/fcmToken:
    post:
      summary: Установка связи токена с МП
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "models.yaml#/components/schemas/PushTokenRequest"
      responses:
          "204":
            description: "Успех"
          default:
            $ref: "../common/errors.yaml#/components/responses/ApiErrorResponse"
    delete:
      summary: Разрыв связи токена с МП
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "models.yaml#/components/schemas/PushDeleteTokenRequest"
      responses:
          "204":
            description: "Успех"
          default:
            $ref: "../common/errors.yaml#/components/responses/ApiErrorResponse"

  /user/registerFcmToken:
    post:
      summary: Сохранение информации о факте запуска приложения через пуш
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "models.yaml#/components/schemas/RegisterPushTokenRequest"
      responses:
          "204":
            description: "Успех"
          default:
            $ref: "../common/errors.yaml#/components/responses/ApiErrorResponse"
